descriptionHtml:
Currently beta.
This one will not be a bodyreplacer but will be added as a custom race. I\'m adding it here to get feedback.

A version with bust closer to the original NBP will come at the real release. At that point these will be custom races.

Would love nice screenies for this one :D

Tell me if it causes any problems that seem unintended.
It is not compatible with other bodymods as it is but rather a series of custom armors will be added for it and as it will not be a mod affecting any NPC\'s you should be alright anyhow.
author: Nalim
